summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed to a portion of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. for street purposes and laying off 39th Ave. S.; and accepting an easement over a portion of vacated 39th Ave. S. adjoining Lot 11, Block 4, Plat of Robinson's Tracts for traffic signalization purposes. (39th Ave. S. at S. Othello St., Traffic Signalization).
